ice 数据的延迟从 `1553ms` 增至 `8541ms` (延迟倍数 ≈5.50)\n\n4. **Frontend 错误状态高频出现**:\n   - 获取广告时，出现 `context deadline exceeded` 错误 (出现4次)\n\n### 异常调用链标识\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"timeout\",\n    \"frontend->currencyservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CurrencyService\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"延迟从2350ms增至12625ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice调用，延迟从8453ms增至131138ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"timeout\",\n      \"evidence\": \"4次 context deadline exceeded 错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"处理CartService请求延迟从1553ms增至8541ms\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 结论\n\n上述数据表明，主要瓶颈位于 CartService (尤其 Checkout 函数) 和 CurrencyService 之间，且 Redis 因调用 CartService 导致显著延迟。Frontend 提供的广告服务因频繁超时返回错误，可能是这些请求等待时间过长，导致超时。建议进一步检查 CartService 和 CurrencyService 的负载情况以及 Redis 的响应能力。"}
